  "text": "01 This image is for illustration only, and the subjects are models; the image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. 02 03 Just because cats can be on their own, doesn't mean that they necessarily like being alone. One of our cats would follow us everywhere if they could. Another one would be purrfectly happy if we only fed them and never spoke to them again. Some cats really crave hooman affection, and as a pawrent, you should give it to them. 04 05 06 07 08 This image is for illustration only, and the subjects are models; the image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. 09 10 11 If this were an occasional thing, we don't think there would be an issue. But constantly asking a roommate to watch your cat is just bad pawrenting. When you get a pet, you agree to put their needs before yours and to give them the best life you can. It doesn't sound like she's doing that for her cat.  12 13 14 15 16 17 18 This image is for illustration only, and the subjects are models; the image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. 19 20 21 22 23 24 25 26 27 Tags Scroll Down For The Next Article",
